---
summary: Home page is confusing and duplicates existing elements
---
created: 2015-03-12 23:48:22.0
creator: jan
description: |-
  It’s a bit confusing what the home page is good for:

  * start chat / join room interface should be rolled into the main chat interface, in the sidebar where it relates to the channels which already exist
  * recent conversations is already the sidebar in the main chat interface
  * the only thing really separate is the »Public rooms« section

  So here’s what could be changed:
  * By default, the chat interface is opened instead of the home page
  * In the sidebar there would be the means to join a new channel, and maybe suggested channels from the public channels
  * The public channels list would be a separate thing you could open, similar to the settings view (also in modal manner, referencing SYWEB-322
